cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.RO 

The paper introduces a novel approach for training policies using reinforcement learning that is backpropagation-free and clock-free. This makes the algorithm more biologically plausible and facilitates distributed implementations. The paper is likely to be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.RO (Robotics).
